:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4314:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle version <code>1.17.9</code> adds a consent prompt option to the Google Maps widget. User consent is required before loading the Google Maps API for sites complying with regulations like DSGVO, or GDPR. The consent prompt settings are located at <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Google Maps: Settings</span></span>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/google-maps-api-consent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">View a demo</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_295602\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-295602\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-295602 size-large\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-699x628.jpg\" alt=\"Google Maps Widget API Consent Settings\" width=\"699\" height=\"628\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-699x628.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-300x270.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-768x690.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-1050x943.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-313x281.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings.jpg 1476w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></p>\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-295602\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Google Maps Widget API Consent Settings</p>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/google-maps-widget/#heading-global-settings\">Google Maps Widget Consent Prompt Documentation</a></p>\n<h3>Enhanced by SiteOrigin Premium</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/map-styles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Premium Map Styles</a> addon provides three additional settings:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Consent prompt text color.</li>\n<li>Consent prompt text background color.</li>\n<li>Consent prompt background image.</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_295599\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-295599\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-699x584.jpg\" alt=\"oogle Maps API Consent Settings\" width=\"699\" height=\"584\" class=\"size-large wp-image-295599\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-699x584.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-300x251.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-768x642.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-1050x877.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-313x262.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings.jpg 1448w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></p>\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-295599\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Consent Prompt Design Settings</p>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/map-styles/#heading-google-maps-api-consent-additional-settings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Premium Google Maps API Consent Additional Settings Documentation</a></p>\n<p>SiteOrigin Premium offers a huge array of additional functionality for Page Builder by SiteOrigin, the SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle, SiteOrigin CSS, and all of our themes. SiteOrigin Premium also includes access to our next-level email support service, perfect for those times when you need fast and effective technical support.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/google-maps-consent-prompt/\">Google Maps Consent Prompt</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://siteorigin.com/google-maps-consent-prompt/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"Rank Math Page Builder Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://siteorigin.com/rank-math-page-builder-support/\